"No, you little" Motormaster screams looking up at his opponent, not seeing
Triggerhappy. The collission between the two titans was incredibly loud,
and painful. Motormaster lay in a heap and rubed his head. "Owwwww. THats
it, time to bring out the big guns". As he finished his sentence he started
to soar upwards into the sky. "Stunticons, regroup" he yelled as loud as he
could.
